In [4]:
def load_img(img_path):
    img = Image.open(img_path)
    img.load()
    return img

class MakeDataset(Dataset):
    def __init__(self, files_path):
        super().__init__()
        self.files_path = files_path
        self.label_encoder = LabelEncoder()
        print(self.files_path[0])
        if 'dataset' in str(self.files_path[0]):
            self.labels = [path.parent.name for path in self.files_path]
            self.label_encoder.fit(self.labels)

    def __len__(self):
        return len(self.files_path)
    
    def __getitem__(self, index):
        image = load_img(self.files_path[index])
        transform = transforms.Compose([transforms.Resize((input_size,input_size)),
                                        transforms.ToTensor()])
        image = transform(image)
        if 'dataset' in str(self.files_path[0]):
            label_str = str(self.files_path[index].parent.name)
            label = self.label_encoder.transform([label_str])
            label = label.item()
            return image, label
        else:
            return image

trainPath = Path('e:/proggit1/mag/sem3/deeplearning/simpson/simpsons_dataset/')
testPath = Path('e:/proggit1/mag/sem3/deeplearning/simpson/kaggle_simpson_testset/')

trainPathIter = sorted(list(trainPath.rglob('*.jpg')))

trainValuelabels = [path.parent.name for path in trainPathIter]
trainFiles, valFiles = train_test_split(trainPathIter, test_size = 0.25, stratify=trainValuelabels)

testFiles = sorted(list(testPath.rglob('*.jpg')))

train_dataset = MakeDataset(trainFiles)
valid_dataset = MakeDataset(valFiles)
test_dataset = MakeDataset(testFiles)

train_loader = DataLoader(dataset=train_dataset, batch_size=batch_size, shuffle=True)
valid_loader = DataLoader(dataset=valid_dataset, batch_size=batch_size, shuffle=False)
test_loader = DataLoader(dataset=test_dataset, batch_size=batch_size, shuffle=True)

def show_imgs(batch_size, dload): 
    f, ax = plt.subplots(int(batch_size / 4), 4, figsize = (12, 12))
    ax = ax.flatten()
    
    # Получение случайного образца из тренировочного датасета
    dataiter = iter(dload)
    images, labels = next(dataiter)
    # Вывод отдельных изображений и их меток классов
    j = 0
    for a in ax:
        npimg = images[j].numpy()
        a.imshow(np.transpose(npimg, (1, 2, 0)))
        a.set_title(classes[labels[j]])
        j+=1
    
    plt.subplots_adjust(left=None, bottom=0.2, right=None, top=None, wspace=None, hspace=None)
    plt.show()

class BasicBlock(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, in_planes, planes, stride=1):
        super(BasicBlock, self).__init__()
        self.block = nn.Sequential(
            nn.Conv2d(in_planes, planes, kernel_size=3, stride=stride, padding=1, bias=False),
            nn.ReLU(),
            nn.MaxPool2d(2)
        )
    def forward(self, x):
        out = self.block(x)
        return out

class ResNet(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, block, num_classes=42):
        super(ResNet, self).__init__()
        self.in_planes = 64
        self.conv1 = nn.Conv2d(3, 32, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1, bias=False)
        self.relu = nn.ReLU()
        self.max_pool = nn.MaxPool2d(2)

        self.blocks = nn.Sequential(block(32, 64, 1), block(64, 128, 1))
        self.blocks1 = nn.Sequential(block(128, 256, 1), block(256, 256, 1))
        self.fc = nn.Linear(16 * 28 * 28, num_classes)
    def forward(self, x):
        out = self.conv1(x)
        out = self.relu(out)
        out = self.max_pool(out)

        out = self.blocks(out)
        out = self.blocks1(out)
        
        out = out.view(out.size(0), -1)
        out = self.fc(out)

        return out

model = ResNet(BasicBlock)
model

  (conv1): Conv2d(3, 32, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), bias=False)
  (relu): ReLU()
  (max_pool): MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2, padding=0, dilation=1, ceil_mode=False)
  (blocks): Sequential(
    (0): BasicBlock(
      (block): Sequential(
        (0): Conv2d(32, 64, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), bias=False)
        (1): ReLU()
        (2): MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2, padding=0, dilation=1, ceil_mode=False)
      )
    )
    (1): BasicBlock(
      (block): Sequential(
        (0): Conv2d(64, 128, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), bias=False)
        (1): ReLU()
        (2): MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2, padding=0, dilation=1, ceil_mode=False)
      )
    )
  )
  (blocks1): Sequential(
    (0): BasicBlock(
      (block): Sequential(
        (0): Conv2d(128, 256, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), bias=False)
        (1): ReLU()
        (2): MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2, padding=0, dilation=1, ceil_mode=False)
      )
    )
    (1): BasicBlock(
      (block): Sequential(
        (0): Conv2d(256, 256, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1), bias=False)
        (1): ReLU()
        (2): MaxPool2d(kernel_size=2, stride=2, padding=0, dilation=1, ceil_mode=False)
      )
    )
  )
  (fc): Linear(in_features=12544, out_features=42, bias=True)

In [13]:
from tqdm import tqdm

# Обучение модели
for epoch in range(epochs):
    start_t = time.time()
    correct = 0
    total = 0
    running_loss = 0.0

    for inputs, labels in tqdm(train_loader, desc='train batches', total = len(train_loader)):
        inputs, labels = inputs.to(device), labels.to(device)
        optimizer.zero_grad()
        outputs = model(inputs)

        _, predicted = torch.max(outputs.data, 1)
        correct += int((predicted == labels).sum())
        
        loss = criterion(outputs, labels)
        loss.backward()
        optimizer.step()

        total += len(outputs)
        running_loss += loss.item()
    end_t = time.time()
    print(f'Epoch = {epoch + 1}, Loss = {running_loss / len(train_loader)}, Time = {end_t - start_t}, Accuracy = {correct / total}')

# Тестирование модели
model.eval()
all_preds = []
all_labels = []

with torch.no_grad():
    for data in valid_loader:
        images, labels = data
        images, labels = images.to(device), labels.to(device)
        outputs = model(images)
        _, preds = torch.max(outputs, 1)
        all_preds.extend(preds.cpu().numpy())
        all_labels.extend(labels.cpu().numpy())

# Вычисление F1-score
f1 = f1_score(all_labels, all_preds, average='weighted')
print(f'F1-score (weighted): {f1}')

def test_illustration(dload, size, mode):
    f, ax = plt.subplots(int(size / 4), 4, figsize = (12, 12))
    ax = ax.flatten()

    if mode:
        dataiter = iter(valid_loader)
        images, labels = next(dataiter)
        images, labels = images.to(device), labels.to(device)
    else:
        dataiter = iter(test_loader)
        images = next(dataiter)
        images = images.to(device)
        
    j = 0
    for a in ax:
        with torch.no_grad():
            output = model(images[j].unsqueeze(0))
            # Преобразование выхода в вероятности классов
            probabilities = torch.nn.functional.softmax(output, dim=1)
            # Получение предсказанного класса
            predicted_class = torch.argmax(probabilities, dim=1)
        pred_p = np.max(probabilities.cpu().numpy()) * 100
        npimg = images[j].cpu().numpy()
        a.imshow(np.transpose(npimg, (1, 2, 0)))
        if mode:
            a.set_title(classes[labels[j]])            
        a.text(5, 60, '{} :\n {}%'.format(classes[predicted_class], pred_p), fontsize = 10, color ='black', backgroundcolor ='white') 
        j+=1
    
    plt.subplots_adjust(left=None, bottom=0.2, right=None, top = None, wspace=None, hspace=None)
    plt.show()
